data.description: 'Welcome to this exquisite Mid-Centry Modern home built by Keller Homes, A Toll Brothers Company. This stunning 4 bed, 3 bath home offers a spacious and all-inclusive living experience. Located in the exclusive Elan neighborhood of the Cordera Community, prepare to be enamored by this beauty, both inside and out. The main level highlights an open floor plan with many high-end finishes, to include: the 42" stainless steel framed gas fireplace in the living room, gourmet kitchen with maple cabinets and oversized island, automated custom window coverings, and white oak hardwood floors with a birch stain throughout the main living area. Head upstairs to the loft where it's a staple for entertaining, or relaxing. Enjoy the breathtaking views of Pikes Peak and the stunning views of the Air Force Academy right off the outdoor balcony. The basement is the perfect set up to enjoy the latest movies with the premium theatre system and 9 ft ceilings. Both bedrooms in the basement offer ample amount of space and walk in closets and one of a kind custom wall painting. Other great features about this home include epoxy coated garage floors, electric dog fence in the backyard, modern five-panel barn doors in the study, shaw carpet, and custom window coverings throughout the whole home. You won't be disappointed when you view this incredible home.
